My personal GNU screen configuration.


INSTALL
=======

To install, do::

    cd ~/
    git clone git://github.com/rdegges/screen.git .screen
    ln -s ~/.screen/screenrc ~/.screenrc
    mkdir -p ~/.screen/{caps,logs}


USAGE
=====

Run `screen` from your terminal, and see the magic.


REFERENCES
==========

http://www.gnu.org/software/screen/manual/screen.html
